0.9 (2014-08-21)
----------------

- Drop support for OCaml < 4
- Replace Cryptokit by Nocrypto
- Replace Lwt_ssl by Tls_lwt for TLS
- Add TLS support for the websocket server
- Replace OASIS by topkg
- Removing camlp4
- Minor interface changes

